}}</ref>。他的前隊友{{Link-en|諾爾貝托·蘇蘭奴|Nolberto Solano}}說，他的能力使他成為球隊中重要的球員<ref>{{en}}{{cite web
|title = Sol hails return of young gun Milner
|publisher = officialplayersites
|url = http://www.officialplayersites.com/players/solano/article.php?id=815
|date = 2006-07-14
|accessdate = 2007-07-29
|archive-date = 2012-04-09
|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66o2YyMXB?url=http://www.officialplayersites.com/players/solano/article.php?id=815
|dead-url = no
}}</ref>。轉會至紐卡素後，米拿仍多出任翼鋒<ref name="position"/>。

米拿亦具備準確傳送和遠射的能力。因此，他由於需要主射[[死球|死球]]而經常去前場，也常常是開[[角球|角球]]和自由球的人選<ref name="everything2">{{en}}{{cite web
|title = James Milner
|publisher = everything2
|url = http://www.everything2.com/index.pl?node_id=1409685
|date = 2003-01-02
|accessdate = 2007-09-12
|archive-date = 2012-04-09
|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66o2kDSeA?url=http://www.everything2.com/index.pl?node_id=1409685
|dead-url = no
}}</ref>。對於他的傳中能力有所爭議，有些體育評述員對此提出批評，其他的記者則說他可以作出準確的傳中<ref>{{en}}{{cite web
